title: GTA+
headline: GTA+
subtitle: This Month’s Benefits
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ Members who've signed up for this month (January 8 - February 4) will also receive:

— Early access to the new Pfister Astrale (Sports Classic)
— 50% off Auto Shop properties and free Style Upgrades
— 2X Rewards on Auto Shop Robbery Contract Finales
— The Pfister Chore Jacket
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
